metadata.name: Tamtaro Complete Setup
metadata.description:
Fully configured AIOStreams setup based on my recommended filters, sort orders, and SEL v2.5.1. Designed for those who want high-quality results with minimal clutter. "Complete Setup" template comes with preconfigured streaming addons and formatter. "Setup Without Addons/Formatter" template will not overwrite current addons/formatter. 
Neither template will overwrite current debrid credentials (click Skip) or proxy settings. For catalogs, refer to my AIOMetadata config over Discord.
metadata.author: Tamtaro
